<template>
    <v-layout>
        <v-btn>
            <v-icon>
                mdi-arrow-left
            </v-icon>

        </v-btn>
        <v-btn v-for="(page, key) in pageList" :key="key">
            {{ page }}</v-btn>
        <v-btn>
            <v-icon>
                mdi-arrow-right
            </v-icon>
        </v-btn>
    </v-layout>
</template>
<script>
export default {
    props: ["data"],
    data() {
        return {
            pageList: []
        }
    },
    mounted() {
        this.init()
    },
    methods: {
        init() {
            if (this.data) {
                this.pageList = []
                for (var i = this.data.startNav; i <= this.data.endNav; i++) {
                    this.pageList.push(i)
                }
            }
        }
    }

}
</script>
<style></style>
